author: The Critical Drinker
description:
She's the woman who cancelled Conan, hired Phoebe Waller-Bridge to do nothing for five years, paid the Russo Brothers $300 Million for a TV show no one wanted, and made the Rings of Power what it is today. And a couple of days ago, her time finally ran out. 

Want to support our Trial By Fire on Kickstarter? Follow this link: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/trialbyfiredrake/trial-by-fire-1/description

Or go to Kickstarter.com and search for Trial By Fire Critical Drinker. Thanks for your suppport!
title: Jennifer Salke Fired - Amazon's Kathleen Kennedy And Her Legacy Of Failure
